features: What Will You Get: you will receive 60 stationery paper and 30 envelopes, plus 48 round dot stickers; 10 Styles with cute lovely design writing stationery paper, each style includes 6 sheets of paper and 3 envelopes, adequate amount and style to meet your daily needs

Proper Size: each stationery writing paper is about 5.5 x 8.2 inch/ 14 x 20.8 cm, each stationery envelope is about 3.3 x 6.5 inch/ 8.5 x 16.4 cm, writing paper fits well in an envelope, appropriate size to use

Quality Materials: the writing paper stationery set is made of quality paper material, strong with no ink bleeding, convenient for you to write smoothly; Colorful round stickers included to meet your sealing need and other uses

Practical Gift: this stationery paper set is a nice gift choice for those who love to write handwritten letters or writing paper collectors; There are some decorations on the edge of the letter paper, which makes the handwriting more impressive and hard to forget

Wide Range of Uses: the letter writing paper and stationary envelope set is suitable for writing letters, and designing business invitations, party invitations, blessing message, greeting notes, thank you notes, etc.; These pretty stationery paper are also suitable for daily writing and sending friends as gifts to increase friendship with each other
body.description: Broad uses: These stationery paper and envelopes can be widely applied to letter writing, sending business invitations, party invitations, blessing message, greeting notes, thank you notes and so on. Suitable for gifts to family and friends who love writing handwritten letters or collecting writing paper. Specifications: Material: paper material Size: Stationery paper: approx. 5.5 x 8.2 inch/ 14 x 20.8 cm Envelope: approx. 3.3 x 6.5 inch/ 8.5 x 16.4 cm Sticker: approx. 0.8 inch/ 2 cm in diameter Color: as shown in the picture Package includes: 60 x Stationery paper 30 x Envelopes 48 x Stickers

reviews.reviewText: I purchased this to write letters to my children who are abroad. I love all the designs and the quantity that comes with each design. I absolutely recommend!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2021
reviews.reviewText: We purchased this for my mother who was in the hospital recovering from a fall/hip surgery. She wanted stationary so she could write letters to her family and friends. She loved all of the patterns that came with the set. Unfortunately she never got to use it. She passed away shortly after she received it due to infection complications. We ended up donating it to Salvation Army but we’re very impressed with the quality. Great product.
